OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FFour of the world's biggest cruise
OL,7,Fliners are to come together for the
OL,8,Ffirst time in a maritime spectacular
OL,9,Fwhich could attract more than a
OL,10,Fmillion people.
OL,12,FNicknamed the Four Queens, the vessels
OL,13,Fwill gather on the River Mersey in May
OL,14,F2028 and coincides with celebrations
OL,15,Fmarking 20 years since Liverpool
OL,16,Fbecame European Capital of Culture.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
