CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776863483
OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FThe city is preparing a year-long
OL,7,Fprogramme of music, maritime and
OL,8,Fsporting events, with Cunard's return
OL,9,Fforming a centrepiece of the
OL,10,Fcelebrations.
OL,12,FThe Queen Mary 2 will set sail from
OL,13,FNew York, the first Cunard ship to
OL,14,Fsail directly between the two cities
OL,15,Fin more than 61 years.
OL,17,FThe luxury cruise line made the
OL,18,Fannouncement on Wednesday 22 April
OL,19,Fahead of tickets for the historic
OL,20,Fcelebration voyages going on sale at a
OL,21,Flater date.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776863483
OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FKatie McAlister, President of Cunard,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Bringing our four Queens
OL,8,Ftogether on the Mersey for the first
OL,9,Ftime will be a rare and incredibly
OL,10,Fspecial moment for Cunard.
OL,12,F"Liverpool is where our story began,
OL,13,Fand returning with the full fleet is a
OL,14,Fpowerful celebration of that bond."
OL,16,FIn May 2015, three of the ships sailed
OL,17,Fin formation towards Liverpool to mark
OL,18,FCunard's 175th anniversary.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
