PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776863483
OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FQueen Mary 2, the largest ocean liner
OL,7,Fever built, performed a choreographed
OL,8,Friver dance alongside the Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth and Queen Victoria before
OL,10,Flining up just 130 metres apart.
OL,12,FNow, following the popularity of the
OL,13,Fnaming of the new Queen Anne ship in
OL,14,FLiverpool in 2024, this new spectacle
OL,15,Fis expected to attract huge crowds to
OL,16,Fboth sides of the river.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
