PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776863483
OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FLast time, an estimated 1.2 to 1.3
OL,7,Fmillion people visited the area to
OL,8,Fwatch the spectacle, complete with a
OL,9,Ffireworks display and a fly past from
OL,10,FThe Red Arrows.
OL,12,FRiver experts have spent time
OL,13,Festablishing the feasibility of
OL,14,Fhosting all four giant vessels in the
OL,15,FMersey at the same time.
OL,17,FThe waterway is only three quarters of
OL,18,Fa mile wide between Liverpool
OL,19,Fwaterfront and Birkenhead's Woodside
OL,20,Fferry terminal, its narrowest point.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
