PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776863483
OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FHarry Doyle, Cabinet Member for
OL,7,FHealth, Wellbeing and Culture at
OL,8,FLiverpool City Council, said, "People
OL,9,Fin our city feel very strong. That
OL,10,Frelationship with our Mersey, with the
OL,11,Fmaritime industry, this is how our
OL,12,Fcity grew.
OL,14,F"To have that spotlight... it just
OL,15,Ffills the city with immense pride."
OL,17,FLiverpool is the birthplace of Cunard,
OL,18,Fwhich is now headquartered in
OL,19,FSouthampton, and as such is seen as
OL,20,Fthe company's spiritual home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
