PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776863483
OL,3,C'World-first river spectacle' could
OL,4,Cattract more than a million people
OL,6,FIts first custom-built ship, the RMS
OL,7,FBritannia, left Liverpool in 1840 on
OL,8,Fits inaugural transatlantic voyage to
OL,9,FHalifax and Boston.
OL,11,FThis marked the beginning of regular
OL,12,Ftransatlantic passenger and mail
OL,13,Fservice.
OL,15,FThe company's headquarters remained in
OL,16,Fthe city until 1967 and the Cunard
OL,17,FBuilding now houses offices for
OL,18,FLiverpool City Council.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
